                <p>
                    <lb n="1r15=54"/> .. Āḷu 
                    <lb n="1r15=55" break="no"/>ṭaiya nāyaṉar <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>paṇṭāra-k-kaṭavuḷarukku Āca 
                    <lb n="1r16=56" break="no"/>ntirākka <hi rend="grantha">stā</hi>yiyāka Aṉupavittu koḷḷa-k kaṭa
                    <lb n="1r17=57" break="no"/>vōr ākavum nammai cā<choice><orig>ṟ</orig><reg>r</reg></choice>nta maṉucar makkaḷ ellārum 
                    <lb n="1r18=58"/>yinta taṟmattukku Oru cillaṟaiyaḷum varāmal tarmat
                    <lb n="1r19=59" break="no"/>tai paripālaṉam paṇṇi uttirōttiramāka naṭappivikka 
                    <lb n="1r20=60"/>k-kaṭavōr ākavum yintapaṭikku Āḷuṭaiya nāyaṉā 
                    <lb n="1r21=61" break="no"/>r <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>paṇṭāra-k-kaṭavuḷarukku maṉappūṟuvamāka Apimāṉi 
                    <lb n="1r22=62" break="no"/><choice><orig>ccu</orig><reg>ttu</reg></choice> caṟuvamāṉiya paṭṭayam paṇṇi-k koṭuttōm 
                    <lb n="1r23=63"/>yinta taṟmattai paripālaṉam paṇṇiṉavarkaḷ keṅ 
                    <lb n="1r24=64" break="no"/>kai-k karaiyilum Āti-cētuvilum puṇṇiya<hi rend="grantha">kṣē</hi>t 
                    <lb n="1r25=65" break="no"/>tiraṅkaḷilum Aṉēkaṅ kōṭi piṟama-piṟitiṭṭaiyum a 
                    <lb n="1r26=66" break="no"/>ṉēkaṅ kōṭi civaliṅka-piṟitiṭṭaiyum paṇṇi 
                    <lb n="1r27=67" break="no"/>ṉa taṟmattai yaṭaiyvār ākavum yinta taṟmattukku 
                    <lb n="1r28=68"/>yātām oruvar vikātañ cillaṟaiyaḷ paṇṇiṉava 
                    <lb n="1r29=69" break="no"/>rkaḷ keṅkaikkaraiyilum Āti-cētuvilum Aṉēka 
                    <lb n="1r30=70" break="no"/>ṅ ‌kōṭi kōvatai paṇṇiṉa tō<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>ttilum mātāpi 
                    <lb n="1r31=71"/>tāvai vataiceyita tō<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>ttilum kōṭi piṟamakatti 
                    <lb n="1r32=72"/>paṇṇiṉa tō<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>ttilum pōka-k kaṭavār ākavum
                    <lb n="1r33=73"/>Intapaṭikki taṟmattukku taṟma-cācaṉa-p-paṭṭayam
                    <lb n="1r34=74"/>paṇṇi koṭuttōm Ēkapperumāḷ-t toṇṭaimā 
                    <lb n="1r35=75" break="no"/>ṉār poṉṉam‌pala toṇṭaimāṉār avarkaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> Ā
                    <lb n="1r36=76" break="no"/>ḷuṭaiya nayiṉār śrī paṇṭārak kaṭavuḷarukku yin 
                    <lb n="1r37=77" break="no"/>ta paṭikku Āvuṭaiya-p pācāri veṭṭeḷuttu
                    
                </p>
                
                
                
                
                
